<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Styles for the overall email */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Styles for the header */
        h1 {
            color: blue;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px 0 12px;
        }

        /* Styles for the paragraphs */
        p {
            color: black;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5em;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }

        /* Styles for the call to action */
        a {
            background-color: blue;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: white;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title %>".</p>
    <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
</body>
</html>